// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - Warden1 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P3925177855" "<color orange>You speak to the Warden in a commanding voice as you administer the serum.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P2363459529" "You WILL do my bidding!"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P1311789652" "<color orange>The Warden's eyes glaze over, followed by a dead stare...</color>"
// Answer Text :
