// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P3692010959" "You found some old Longbow documents!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - TaskSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P2107497240" "You've left the Longbow base in ruins - thanks to the help of these willing Longbow Wardens!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - ReturnSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// RandomFameString :
"P602850750" "I heard all about Longbow's new experimental serum - is that even legal? If they're not the good guys, who is supposed to stand against {HeroName}?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Rog_SL4-5_Task_02 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Spirit 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2908843576" "Very Annoyed Spirit"
// DetailString :
"P1531828321" "You destroyed an odd case within the old warehouse. Upon its destruction, a spirit shot out of it, looking very annoyed - at you! It circled around you for a few moments before saying these words...<br><br><color CadetBlue>You! You're the one who... oh no, wait, maybe it wasn't you. Was it? Maybe it was another you...or someone else entirely. Regardless, look, this chaos? Not good. You heard of Lughebu? God of the Banished Pantheon? Bah! You wouldn't care. Your type never does. All I'm saying is that you should steer clear of Dark Astoria. No one can stop what's happening there now.</color><br><br>With that, the spirit vanishes."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P636234992" "It's not too difficult to track down information on where Longbow's latest serum is being made. Most agents that would have tried to stop you are too busy tracking down these Wardens and cleaning up the mess that is being left in their wake.<br><br>Surprisingly enough, you find that the serum is being made in an abandoned warehouse. Wyvern and the Legacy Chain have been called in for guard duty on the warehouse while Longbow are out and about.<br><br>It'll be a simple manner of getting in there, getting the serum, and then getting out."
// AcceptString :
"P1260253985" "Find Longbow's serum and sell it for the highest price!"
// SendOffString :
"P1430972731" "You'll have to hurry to take advantage of the current situation - once Longbow have their Wardens back, they'll be sending their full force to check on their boys here."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2691605373" "Steal the Longbow serum!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1992830115" "Wyvern you could kind of understand guarding the serum, but Legacy Chain? Longbow must be getting desperate."
// TaskTitle :
"P3302682459" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Vial of Pulsating Liquid</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P697573956" "The warehouse seems like no one has walked in here in ages. Clever on Longbow's part, but not clever enough to fool you."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3637549976" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Vial of Pulsating Liquid</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You managed to steal the remains of serum numbers 4 and 5. Within moments of informing your contacts of your find, you have several possible buyers, all of them paying top dollar.<br><br>You also overhear that Longbow was able to apprehend the Wardens that they lost control of. They'll be in for a rude surprise when they get back to that warehouse, that's for sure."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Variable - VILLAIN_GROUP 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Variable - INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P4018506934" "Keep an eye out for anything strange."

