// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vil_SL4-5_Task_04 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P2280417535" "<color orange>The weapon's system activates as you follow the steps written down in the codebook.</color><br><br><color BurlyWood>WEAPONS SYSTEM ACTIVATED.<br><br> WELCOME ARCHON ARCADIO. <br><br>PLEASE SELECT AN OPERATION FROM BELOW."
// Answer Text :
"P3232675457" "ASSIGN TARGET"
// Answer Text :
"P158688648" "DISPLAY TECHNICAL INFORMATION"
// Answer Text :
"P3326752765" "DISPLAY PREVIOUS TARGETS"
// Answer Text :
"P4085482278" "SHUT DOWN"
// Page Menu Text :
"P2508940898" "<color BurlyWood>WEAPONS SYSTEM ACTIVE.<br><br> WELCOME ARCHON ARCADIO. <br><br>PLEASE SELECT AN OPERATION FROM BELOW."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P159637832" "<color BurlyWood>PLEASE ASSIGN AN AREA TO SCAN FOR POSSIBLE TARGETS.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P1694222397" "(Assign the area where the Longbow Cruiser is)"
// Page Cruiser Text :
"P623290148" "<color BurlyWood>FOLLOWING TARGETS FOUND:<br><br>Longbow Cruiser x 1.<br><br>PLEASE SELECT AN ACTION"
// Answer Text :
"P805862251" "DESTROY TARGET"
// Page Destroy Text :
"P2640635451" ""<color BurlyWood>DESTROYING...PLEASE WAIT...</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P688811988" "...."
// Page Wait Text :
"P3102984231" "<color BurlyWood>...</color>"
// Page Soon Text :
"P1824799982" "<color BurlyWood>........</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P698492072" "...seriously? How long is this going-"
// Page Done Text :
"P4152899558" "<color BurlyWood>TARGET DESTROYED.<br><br>ERROR. MAIN WEAPON SYSTEM MALFUNCTION.<br><br>INITIATING SHUTDOWN TO PREVENT SELF-DESTRUCTION. <br><br>COUNCIL ENGINEER WILL BE ALERTED."
// Answer Text :
"P3357844881" "(Hack the system to cause a self-destruct)"
// Page Destruct Text :
"P1659529994" "<color orange>You hack the computer and are able to force it - and the weapon's system - to self-destruct!"
// Answer Text :
"P3532647996" "A shame dealings with computers end this way a lot."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P3545981978" "<color BurlyWood>INFORMATION:<br><br>WEAPON DESIGNER: ARCHON BURKHOLDER<br><br>WEAPON PROGRAMMER: VANDAL<br><br>ORDERED BY: REQUIEM"
// Answer Text :
"P1452389042" "MAIN MENU"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P3277793209" "<color BurlyWood>PREVIOUS TARGETS:<br><br>Council Base PROGRAMMER NOTE: Empty base as assured by Requiem.<br><br>Longbow Base<br><br>Supposed location of Midnighter Club.<br><br>Other supposed location of Midnighter Club*<br><br>Abandoned Library.<br><br>*NOTE: IF YOU ARE ASSIGNED TO BLOW UP A LOCATION OF MIDNIGHTER CLUB, PLEASE DOUBLE CHECK ORDERS DIRECTLY WITH ARAKHN."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Codes 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1268243546" "A Threat and the Codes"
// DetailString :
"P2226123267" "You defeated Archon Arcadio and retrieved the other half of the codebook, which would give you full access to the weapon's system inside the Council base.<br><br>Unfortunately, Arcadio alerted a Longbow Cruiser nearby to the location of the base, willing to sacrifice the rest of his men to see you fry.<br><br>Not that you're going to fry, of course. You'll just have to put this weapon's system to use - what better target then a Longbow cruiser brimming with people looking to arrest you?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1593705695" "You've already gotten ahold of one half of the codes to access the weapon system, but you'll need to get the other half.  It's no big jump to think the owner will have it in his or her possession.<br><br>Once you have the codes and the info in your possession, then you can move on to bigger and better plans - like blowing up anyone who dares to get in your way!"
// AcceptString :
"P319244341" "Find the owner of the codebook, get the codes and whereabouts of the complex."
// SendOffString :
"P3673337468" "Since you already know where the hideout of the codebook owner is, there's no need to waste time.  Go there and find the spy and make him or her tell you what you need to know."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3033800457" "Find the other half of the codes to access the weapon!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P146508877" "Go find the person who is holding the other half of the codebook!"
// TaskTitle :
"P292087518" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Annotated Codebook</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3881166096" "You'll have to find whoever has the other half of the codebook first. With any luck, the key to controlling the weapon's system will be here as well."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3718694028" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Annotated Codebook</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You can see some smoke rising off in the distance - smoke from the destroyed Longbow Cruiser.<br><br>You look at the current news to see that the PPD are trying to contain an explosion within Brickstown - which is where this facility must have originally been."

