// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Rog_SL4-5_Task_04 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Answer Text :
"P1849984905" "(Begin procedure to shut down)"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P3639286182" "<color orange>You enter the proper codes to initiate the shutdown sequence. A series of numbers appear on screen before legible text appears.</color><br><br><color BurlyWood>SHUT DOWN SEQUENCE ACTIVATED. <br><br>PLEASE BE AWARE THAT THIS WILL HALT ALL OPERATIONS OF THE WEAPON SYSTEM. <br><br>TO CONTINUE, PLEASE ANSWER INITIAL SECURITY QUESTION. <br><br>PLEASE ENTER WHO THE WEAPON DESIGNER FOR THIS PROGRAM WAS."
// Answer Text :
"P614729829" "Archon Burkholder"
// Answer Text :
"P2594690832" "Vandal"
// Page Wrong Text :
"P3301401561" "<color BurlyWood>INCORRECT. SHUTTING DOWN.</color>"
// Page Burkholder Text :
"P1447614736" "<color BurlyWood>CORRECT.<br><br>INITIALIZING NEXT STEP.<br><br>PLEASE ANSWER THE FOLLOWING SECURITY QUESTION.<br><br>PLEASE ENTER WHO ORDERED THE WEAPON PROGRAM TO BE CREATED."
// Answer Text :
"P66753318" "The Center"
// Answer Text :
"P2026798565" "Requiem"
// Page Requiem Text :
"P251269286" "<color BurlyWood>CORRECT.<br><br>INITIALIZING FINAL STEP.<br><br>PLEASE INPUT THE LAST TARGET IN WHICH THIS SYSTEM WAS ASSIGNED TO FIRE UPON."
// Answer Text :
"P502610359" "Abandoned Library"
// Answer Text :
"P2429180204" "The Midnighter's Club"
// Answer Text :
"P3725647690" "Longbow Base"
// Page Library Text :
"P2427549610" "<color BurlyWood>CORRECT.<br><br>SYSTEM SHUTTING DOWN.<br><br>....<br><br>.....<br><br>SHUTDOWN COMPLETE.<br><br>HAIL THE COUNCIL.<br><br>HAVE A NICE DAY."
// Answer Text :
"P292451403" "Huh. Well, there you go."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Codes 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// DetailString :
"P686059373" "You defeated Archon Arcadio and retrieved the other half of the codebook, which would give you full access to the weapon's system inside the Council base.<br><br>Unfortunately, Arcadio alerted a Longbow Cruiser nearby to the location of the base, willing to sacrifice the rest of his men to see you fry.<br><br>While it would be simple to put this weapon's system to use, the aftereffects would be too unpredictable. You'll just have to shut it down before Longbow gets here!<br><br>You flip through the codebook and find a page describing the shut-down process.<br><br>'Vandal said that if worse comes to worse, he put in an emergency shut down procedure. It's simple enough, just access it with the code mentioned below. But to activate it we'd need to answer some security questions first.'"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2474157092" "After re-reading what this weapon is capable of, you're not too sure you'd be around if this thing goes off prematurely.  Sure, it could put you in pretty high standing within the Rogue Isles, but if something goes wrong you just might get blown sky high.  Or worse yet, someone else could cause it to go critical.  It's best if this was out of everyone's hands.<br><br>The only way to do that would be to find the other half of the codebook and use it to shut down the weapon's system."
// AcceptString :
"P3079643588" "Find where the codes are kept and destroy them before real damage is caused!"
// SendOffString :
"P109678830" "Since you already know where the hideout of the codebook owner is, there's no need to waste time.  Get over there and find where he or she is keeping the other half, then use it to shut down the weapon's system for good."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1027638526" "Shut down the weapon's system!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2888440266" "This won't exactly earn you any money, but it'll ensure that you're not blown up in the future <i>while</i> earning money."
// TaskTitle :
"P108038410" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Annotated Codebook</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2688829517" "The owner of the codebook will likely have kept it secured inside a safe container.  You may have to destroy the container to get the codebook, as well."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1587288346" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Annotated Codebook</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You were able to shut down the weapon's system and avoid Longbow bearing down on you.<br><br>Just as you managed to get clear of the base, a large fleet of Longbow stormed in. That'll lead to some big problems for the Council - fortunately, none of it will lead back to you."

