// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3839066752" "Steven Werner sounds like he's in a lot of trouble. You know that saving him will mean a gigantic payday and access to probably any item you could think of. It might also get you some higher up connections - he has to hire someone to get those artifacts, right?  <br><br>Taking up Werner's offer will mean more opportunities for you in the future - despite angering the Family."
// AcceptString :
"P1192690793" "Take down Paulie 'The Gun Show' Morrini to help Steven Werner."
// SendOffString :
"P220882241" "You have a good idea of where you can track down Paulie Morrini - it's never too hard to find the Family around Sharkhead Isle. Now it's time to send him the right message - for a price, of course."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2657297795" "Defeat Paulie 'The Gun Show' Morrini!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3087236709" "You head to the last known location of Paulie Morrini."
// TaskTitle :
"P1828436179" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Stuttered Plea For Help</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3800587412" "You overhear orders being shouted to members of the Family. They sound concerned - you might not be alone here."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P22609406" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Stuttered Plea For Help</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You beat down Paulie Morrini and managed to get the Family off of Steven Werner's case. You've already been contaced by Werner regarding a healthy payment for helping him out of this jam."

