"P3223573451" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Nearby Sobbing Scrapyarder</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You rescued the leaders of the Scrapyarders, who were extremely thankful. One of them even gave you some spare pieces of red coral shards they collected. Who said charity doesn't pay off?"

