"P1498808664" "Pantheon's Activation"
// DetailString :
"P578423448" "You found several powerful artifacts within the Banished Pantheon lair. However, this caused their lair to come alive! You'll have to fight your way through to get out."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P364520277" "The plight of some Family member is beneath you, as is finding some cure to sell to them. No, you're not about the money - you're about the <color red>power!</color> The Banished Pantheon aren't a common sight in Sharkhead Isle, meaning it shouldn't be too hard to track them down. Worst case scenario, you find a few simple artifacts that you can use on the next conflict that gives you some problems. Best case scenario, you find the next Malleus Mundi."
// AcceptString :
"P1275294" "Steal the Banished Pantheon's Artifacts!"
// SendOffString :
"P2524071075" "You head off to the possible location of the Banished Pantheon. This should be interesting."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P899409638" "Raid the Banished Pantheon lair!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P65660325" "Maybe you'll even find the artifact to control the cursed Family member."
// TaskTitle :
"P3990895049" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Curse of the Curious Mook</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2995386338" "You pass through the dark caverns to enter the Banished Pantheon lair. The cavern seems quiet...but you're sure this is the only place the Pantheon could be."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1663426655" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Curse of the Curious Mook</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You exit the Banished Pantheon lair with a good haul of artifacts - now it's just a matter of finding which one does what and using them to their full potential."

