// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - ExplosivesPlanted 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1774891693" "The countdown begins..."
// DetailString :
"P1863764372" "You've given yourself plenty of time to set up these explosives and to get out.  It's satisfying to know that you'll be eliminating a hive of pesky vermin and causing fear within their ranks."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - AlarmSounded 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3957797187" "Fuscia Alert!"
// DetailString :
"P275254216" "A piercing klaxon fills the air.  You can hear the sound of armored bootfalls headed your way."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3840469468" "It's pathetic, really, how Wyvern has let their guard down, pouring nearly all of their resources into such a desperate ploy.  And kidnapping an Arachnos dignitary?  Really?  How did they think this would turn out?  <br><br>Perhaps turning one of their hideouts into a <color red>smoldering crater</color> will teach them to not interfere with what goes on in the Rogue Isles.  If not, hey, at least you got to cause some mayhem."
// AcceptString :
"P807914457" "Destroy the vulnerable Wyvern hideout!"
// SendOffString :
"P1248147282" "You take note of the Wyvern hideout's coordinates."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1249723006" "Destroy the Wyvern hideout!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P436217659" "Hideout coordinates?  Check!  Explosives?  Check!  It's time to cause some destruction!"
// TaskTitle :
"P1153409339" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Interrogation Results</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P602270114" "Just as you predicted.  Security will be lighter than it normally would be, but it looks like there's still a fair amount of Wyvern in here.  Oh well, more pain to inflict."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3876266698" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Interrogation Results</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Well, that was satisfying.  In just a matter of moments the countdown will reach zero, turning this old office into a blazing inferno."

