// Clue Name :
"P1873251226" "The Arachnos Dignitary says..."
// DetailString :
"P825741514" "Hey, thanks!  I've opened the safe for you, take whatever you want."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P851500394" "It doesn't matter whether this Arachnos dignitary lives or dies, but you see an opportunity to not only get paid, but to also gain favor with Arachnos.  So, you get to kill two birds with one stone.  Get a big payday and get those Arachnos jerks off your back."
// AcceptString :
"P1551449533" "Liberate the Arachnos dignitary for a fee."
// SendOffString :
"P2535114843" "You head off to the Arachnos base. It's time for a big payday.  It's only a matter of time before things escalate."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P173267382" "Liberate the Arachnos dignitary from Wyvern"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1373991548" "You've got the location of the Arachnos base and you know the Arachnos dignitary is still inside.  The sooner you get in there and liberate the dignitary, the better."
// TaskTitle :
"P3594864826" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Interrogation Results</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2544932036" "You hear the voice of a Wyvern agent demanding the release of some of his men, and a sharp refusal from an Arachnos official over a radio."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P638522349" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Interrogation Results</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You've lead the Arachnos dignitary to safety, only to have him whisked away by Arachnos soldiers.  Hey... at least you got paid.  Hopefully Arachnos recognizes what you've done here today and at least cuts you some slack in the near future."

